sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Customer)
    participant WB as WhatsAppBot
    participant MA as MetaAPI
    participant CG as ChatGPTAPI
    participant DB as Database
    participant AD as Admin
    participant DA as DashboardApp
    participant NS as Notification
    participant EM as EmailSender

    U->>MA: Send WhatsApp message (registration/booking)
    MA->>WB: Forward webhook event
    WB->>DB: Check customer registration
    alt Not registered
        WB->>U: Prompt registration
        U->>WB: Send registration info
        WB->>DB: Add customer
        WB->>U: Confirm registration
    else Registered
        WB->>CG: Get ChatGPT response (conversation/booking intent)
        CG-->>WB: Return response
        WB->>DB: Create booking (if booking intent)
        WB->>U: Send booking confirmation
    end
    WB->>NS: Send notification (WhatsApp/email)
    NS->>MA: Send WhatsApp notification
    NS->>EM: Send email notification

    AD->>DA: Login to dashboard
    DA->>DB: Authenticate admin
    DA->>DB: Fetch bookings/notifications
    DA->>AD: Show bookings/notifications
    AD->>DA: Update booking status/send notification
    DA->>DB: Update booking status
    DA->>NS: Send notification
    NS->>MA: Send WhatsApp notification
    NS->>EM: Send email notification